{"article_id":"yNYqFZD94YrngQkP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In a sharp but expected departure from US policy , President Trump said Friday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"he would decertify the deal on Iran ' s nuclear program","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"and kick it back to Congress","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"so lawmakers could make it tougher .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"\" As president of United States , my highest obligation is to ensure the safety and security of the American people , \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the president said ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that he is determined","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that \" Iran will never get a nuclear weapon . \"","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Trump wants lawmakers to change legislation","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"- known as the Iran Nuclear Agreement Review Act -","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that requires the president to certify every 90 days","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that Iran is in compliance with the 2015 deal .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The president railed against Iran ' s \" destabilizing influence \" in the Middle East , \" particularly its support for terrorism and militants . \"","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Iran vowed , meanwhile , to retaliate against any action","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"targeting its armed forces ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and accused the US of violating the spirit of the nuclear deal .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"\" Iran will strongly respond to any action against its military forces ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"including the Revolutionary Guards Corps , \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Foreign Ministry spokesman Bahram Qasemi said Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Reuters reported .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that Iran would continue to expand its defensive power","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"- including its ballistic missile program .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Rework the deal","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to make it harder for Iran to develop a nuclear weapon .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Ensure","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that it addresses the Islamic theocracy ' s ballistic missile program","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to lessen the threat of attacks on Israel and other nations .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Counter Iranian support for terrorists and other bad actors in the region","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"the White House says","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"contribute to Mideast instability .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The complicated move puts the Trump administration on a political and diplomatic tightrope .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"The US will technically remain in the pact","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"even though Trump ' s repeatedly slammed it as \" embarrassing \" and the \" worst deal ever . \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"by refusing to certify the merits of the deal ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"he ' s putting its fate on lawmakers ' shoulders","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and asking them to deliver something","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"the GOP-led Congress has failed to give him","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"- a major piece of legislation .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"But Secretary of State Rex Tillerson was wary about the prospects of a new accord .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"\" What we are laying out here is this is the pathway","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"we think","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"provides us the best platform","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"from which to attempt to fix this deal .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"We may be unsuccessful .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"We may not be able to fix it .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"if we ' re not ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"then we may end up out of the deal , \"","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Reuters reported .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Trump wants Congress to pass new legislation within three months","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"to automatically reimpose tough sanctions","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"if Iran crosses certain lines","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"related to nuclear activity and its ballistic missile program .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The administration hopes","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"the move will pressure other parties to the deal","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"- Britain , China , France , Germany and Russia -","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to open talks on a new deal .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"But all of them have urged the US not to pull out of the accord ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"it can not be renegotiated","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"- as have many Democrats and Republicans alike in Congress .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Trump also announced","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that the Treasury Department would impose new sanctions against people","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"involved with the Iranian Revolutionary Guards ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"he says","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"supports terrorists .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"The International Atomic Energy Agency , the UN body","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"charged with monitoring the nuclear deal ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"has repeatedly said","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Iran is in compliance with the deal ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and Trump had certified it twice already in his nascent presidency .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"In response to the president ' s action , lawmakers can do nothing ,","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"pass Trump ' s new legislation ,","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"or choose to reinstate all the Iran sanctions","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"and effectively blow up the pact .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Trump ' s actions on the Iran deal have made lawmakers uneasy","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"- even those","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"who were strongly opposed to the nuclear pact .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"\" As flawed as the deal is ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"I believe","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"we must now enforce the hell out of it , \"","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"House Foreign Affairs Committee Chairman Ed Royce","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"said Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"\" Let ' s do it right , \"","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Iran deal opponent Rep. Eliot Engel","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"said Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"\" Don ' t blow up the agreement","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"to save it .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"We ' ll come out worse in the end . ...","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"But this talk","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"of decertifying the agreement ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"then kicking it to Congress for some sort of magical fix","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"just doesn ' t make sense . \"","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Meanwhile , a pair of top Republicans unveiled a plan Friday","depth":3},{"id":102,"text":"to carry out Trump ' s directive","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"to change the law","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"that requires him to certify Iran ' s compliance with the nuclear deal every 90 days .","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"The bill , from Senate Foreign Relations Chairman Bob Corker","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"( R-Tenn. )","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"and Iran hawk Sen. Tom Cotton","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"( R-Ark . ) ,","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"is intended to address issues","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"they see in the nuclear deal itself ,","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"according to a fact sheet from Corker ' s office .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":212,"right":222,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":212,"left":165,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"